title: America's Greatest Hits - History (1975)
description:
History: America's Greatest Hits is the first compilation album by American folk rock trio America, released by Warner Bros. Records in December 1975. The first seven tracks of the album, having been recorded prior to producer George Martin's involvement with the group, were remixed by Martin for this release.
The album was a big hit in the US, reaching number 3 on the Billboard album chart and being certified MULTI-PLATINUM by the RIAA.
[Source: Wikipedia]

Original Release Year: 1975
Genre: Rock/Pop
